 a monthly detailed list of shipments commercialized by SNPC on behalf of the government, including information on the type of product, the date of loading, the recipient, the number of barrels and the selling price (in US dollars and CFAF) as well as the date of receipt of the sale proceeds by the Treasury; and actual and projected quarterly data to determine the required subsidies in the fuel sector, including prices, quantities, and costs.

